# Data Schemas

This project uses Zod for runtime type validation and TypeScript for static type checking.

## Key Schemas
- [patient-schema.ts](mdc:src/schemas/patient-schema.ts) - Patient information schema and types

## Schema Patterns
- Zod schemas define validation rules
- TypeScript types are derived from schemas using `z.infer<typeof schema>`
- Schemas are used for API validation and AI data structuring